<inglise> - inspections carried out by the competent authority, with its own instruments, of measurements taken with the instruments installed by the undertaking. </inglise>
<eesti> - p&auml;deva asutuse enda seadmetega kontrollida ettev&otilde;tte paigaldatud seadmete m&otilde;&otilde;tmistulemusi. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 7 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 7 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Samples of the products enumerated in Article 6 (1) (b) to (f) may be taken for the purposes of analysis. </inglise>
