<eesti> Artikkel 9 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Inspectors may take note of written and documentary material held by the natural and legal persons at the various stages enumerated in Article 4 (3). </inglise>
